Debian on Raspberry pi 4

https://wiki.debian.org/RaspberryPi4
https://raspi.debian.net/
https://raspi.debian.net/tested-images/

Use etcher or raspberry pi imager to write the image onto the sdcard or drive

login : root without any password

# Installing common softwares
apt install wget curl gcc bison autoconf python golang etc...

# sshd change the config to allow root to login or create a user instead